fields.Alias: Alias, usually a shortened version of the agent's name
fields.ProfileId: ID of the user profile, typically 'Standard User' or a similar profile
fields.Username: Unique username for the agent in Salesforce

fields.Name: Name of the account
fields.NumberOfEmployees: Number of employees in the account

fields.ClosedDate: Date when the case was closed in 'YYYY-MM-DDTHH:MM:SSZ' format
fields.ContactId: ID of the contact associated with this case. References Contact object
fields.CreatedDate: Date when the case was created in 'YYYY-MM-DDTHH:MM:SSZ' format
fields.IssueId__c: ID of the Issue associated with this case
fields.OrderItemId__c: ID of the Order Item associated with this case
fields.OwnerId: The latest owner of the case. References User object
fields.Status: Status of the case, e.g., 'New', 'Working', 'Escalated', etc
fields.Subject: Subject of the case

fields.CatalogId: ID of the catalog this category belongs to
fields.Name: Name of the product category

fields.IsActive: Boolean to mark if the product is active
fields.Name: Name of the product

fields.Id: ID of the product category product

fields.IsActive: Boolean to mark if the price book is active
fields.Name: Name of the price book
fields.ValidFrom: Start date for the price book in 'YYYY-MM-DDTHH:MM:SSZ' format
fields.ValidTo: End date for the price book in 'YYYY-MM-DDTHH:MM:SSZ' format

fields.Id: ID of the price book entry
fields.Pricebook2Id: ID of the price book this entry belongs to. References Pricebook2 object
fields.Product2Id: ID of the product associated with this price book entry. References Product2 object

fields.AccountId: ID of the customer account. References Account object
fields.EffectiveDate: Effective date of the order in 'YYYY-MM-DD' format
fields.OwnerId: ID of the agent who owns the order. References User object
fields.Pricebook2Id: ID of the price book this order belongs to. References Pricebook2 object
fields.Status: Status of the order, typically 'Draft' or 'Activated'

fields.OrderId: ID of the order this item belongs to. References Order object
fields.PriceBookEntryId: ID of the price book entry for this order item. References PricebookEntry object
fields.Product2Id: ID of the product associated with this order item. References Product2 object

fields.MessageDate: Timestamp when the message was sent in 'YYYY-MM-DDTHH:MM:SSZ' format
fields.ParentId: ID of the case related to this email. References Case object
fields.RelatedToId: ID that links to objects like Opportunity and Case. Identical to ParentId when associated with a case. References Case and Opportunity objects.
fields.Subject: Subject of the email

fields.AccountId: ID of the customer account. References Account object
fields.CaseId: ID of the case related to this chat. References Case object
fields.Id: ID of the live chat transcript
fields.OwnerId: ID of the agent who owned the chat. References User object

fields.CaseId__c: ID of the case this history entry is related to. References Case object
fields.CreatedDate: The date when this change was made, in 'YYYY-MM-DDTHH:MM:SSZ' format
fields.Field__c: Specifies the field or type of change. One of ['Case Creation', 'Owner Assignment', 'Case Closed']
fields.NewValue__c: The new value after the change. References User object if the type of change is 'Owner Assignment' else null
fields.OldValue__c: The previous value before the change. References User object if the type of change is 'Owner Assignment' else null

fields.AccountId: ID of the customer account. References Account object
fields.Amount: Monetary value of the opportunity in the default currency
fields.CloseDate: Expected close date of the opportunity
fields.ContactId: ID of the contact associated with this opportunity. References Contact object
fields.ContractID__c: ID of the contract associated with this opportunity. References Contract object
fields.CreatedDate: Date when the opportunity was created, in 'YYYY-MM-DDTHH:MM:SSZ' format
fields.Name: Name of the opportunity
fields.OwnerId: ID of the agent who owns the opportunity. References User object
fields.StageName: Stage of the opportunity. One of ['Qualification', 'Discovery', 'Quote', 'Negotiation', 'Closed']

fields.Id: ID of the opportunity line item
fields.OpportunityId: ID of the opportunity associated with this line item. References Opportunity object
fields.PricebookEntryId: ID of the price book entry for this line item. References PricebookEntry object
fields.Product2Id: ID of the product associated with this line item. References Product2 object
fields.TotalPrice: Total price of the product. Calculated as Quantity * UnitPrice * (1 - Discount/100)

fields.AccountId: ID of the customer account. References Account object
fields.ContactId: ID of the contact associated with this quote. References Contact object
fields.CreatedDate: Date when the quote was created, in 'YYYY-MM-DDTHH:MM:SSZ' format
fields.ExpirationDate: Expiration date of the quote, in 'YYYY-MM-DDTHH:MM:SSZ' format
fields.Name: Name of the quote
fields.OpportunityId: ID of the opportunity associated with this quote. References Opportunity object
fields.Status: Status of the quote. One of ['Draft', 'Needs Review', 'In Review', 'Approved', 'Rejected', 'Presented', 'Accepted', 'Denied']

fields.Id: ID of the quote line item
fields.OpportunityLineItemId: ID of the opportunity line item associated with this quote line item. References OpportunityLineItem object
fields.PricebookEntryId: ID of the price book entry for this line item. References PricebookEntry object
fields.Product2Id: ID of the product associated with this line item. References Product2 object
fields.QuoteId: ID of the quote associated with this line item. References Quote object
fields.TotalPrice: Total price of the product. Calculated as Quantity * UnitPrice * (1 - Discount/100)

fields.AccountId: ID of the customer account. References Account object
fields.CompanySignedDate: Date when the company signed the contract, in 'YYYY-MM-DD' format
fields.ContractTerm: Duration of the contract in months
fields.CustomerSignedDate: Date when the customer signed the contract, in 'YYYY-MM-DD' format
fields.Description: Detailed description of the contract terms and conditions
fields.StartDate: Date when the contract becomes effective, in 'YYYY-MM-DD' format
fields.Status: Status of the contract. One of ['In approval Process', 'Activated', 'Draft', 'Rejected', 'Negotiating', 'Awaiting Signature', 'Signature Declined', 'Signed', 'Canceled', 'Contract Terminated']

fields.Body__c: Content of the voice call transcript
fields.CreatedDate: Date when the voice call transcript was created, in 'YYYY-MM-DDTHH:MM:SSZ' format
fields.EndTime__c: Timestamp when the voice call transcript ended, in 'YYYY-MM-DDTHH:MM:SSZ' format
fields.Id: ID of the voice call transcript
fields.LeadId__c: ID of the lead associated with this voice call transcript. References Lead object
fields.OpportunityId__c: ID of the opportunity associated with this voice call transcript. References Opportunity object

fields.ActivityDate: Date when the task is due, in 'YYYY-MM-DDTHH:MM:SSZ' format
fields.OwnerId: ID of the agent who owns the task. References User object
fields.Priority: Priority of the task. One of ['Low', 'Medium', 'High', 'Urgent']
fields.Status: Status of the task. One of ['Not Started', 'In Progress', 'Completed', 'Deferred', 'Waiting']
fields.Subject: Subject of the task
fields.WhatId: ID of the opportunity associated with this task. References Opportunity object

fields.DurationInMinutes: Duration of the event in minutes
fields.IsAllDayEvent: Boolean to mark if the event is an all-day event
fields.OwnerId: ID of the agent who owns the event. References User object
fields.StartDateTime: Start datetime of the event, in 'YYYY-MM-DDTHH:MM:SSZ' format
fields.Subject: Subject of the event
fields.WhatId: ID of the opportunity associated with this event. References Opportunity object

fields.Description: A comma separated list of territories/states (e.g. CA,IL,AL)
fields.Name: Name of the territory

fields.Id: ID of the user territory association
fields.Territory2Id: ID of the territory associated with the agent. References Territory2 object
fields.UserId: ID of the agent who is associated with the territory. References User object

fields.ConvertedAccountId: ID of the Account record created when the Lead is converted. References Account object
fields.ConvertedContactId: ID of the Contact record created when the Lead is converted. References Contact object
fields.ConvertedDate: Date when the lead was converted in 'YYYY-MM-DD' format
fields.CreatedDate: Date when the lead was created in 'YYYY-MM-DDTHH:MM:SSZ' format
fields.IsConverted: Boolean indicating whether the lead has been converted
fields.OwnerId: ID of the agent who owns the lead. References User object
fields.Status: Status of the lead. One of ['New', 'Contacted', 'Qualified', 'Proposal', 'Negotiation', 'Closed']
fields.Title: Job title of the lead
